edBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T04:22:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>月牙天衝</blockquote><br />\n唔係紅蓮天衝咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n黑崎一護wor"},{"pid":"aca00a1e97ec671e055326183358e590442bb1e6","tid":247592,"uid":88812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T04:33:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中醫昆鳩人...又唔見西醫咁講？</blockquote><br />\n現今科學好多嘢都解釋唔到，唔好以為西醫就啱哂先得㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a647ca2d64426db6ae9ec4c33d0544d434e1006f","tid":247592,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T05:54:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>rip<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中醫昆鳩人...又唔見西醫咁講？</blockquote><br />\n現今科學好多嘢都解釋唔到，唔好以為西醫就啱哂先得㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比我自慰下ok?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da5cdaadd4278099e09fefebbab3aba1abef6cd","tid":247592,"uid":1496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T05:57:50.000Z","msg":"十隻手指都有 <br />\n肥仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b76716b6f41e9b6dbe86ce67ea72decca1dcf1","tid":247592,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T06:04:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十隻手指都有 <br />\n肥仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來唔健康既人先有<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n死肥Doi<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ed6db7b2f6e924ff1c9cb15828bfb719783dbe2","tid":247592,"uid":8867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T06:05:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a69d9a39297ec4039c72b13197f385c789e8fbef","tid":247592,"uid":20362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T06:07:20.000Z","msg":"聽講係唔健康先有喎<br />\n細個有 大個冇晒<br />\n但又唔覺有咩分別"},{"pid":"3f343a21751426cb1899652ea0785f0882123d99","tid":247592,"uid":73583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T06:07:55.000Z","msg":"因為身體唔係幾好<br />\n之前睇中醫調理左一排<br />\n個陣月牙係真係見到明顯升高左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但無睇之後就慢慢跌返<br />\n問過中醫佢話月牙多係代表健康<br />\n<br />\n我都一直有留意月牙呢個問題<br />\n我留意到上莊上到個樣又殘又暗既人個月牙都真係好少幾乎無<br />\n所以我都信月牙多係健康<br />\n<br />\n利申:成日留意人地個月牙去求證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b33325c3cb08e09a89d7836bb8bb23e70ca9914","tid":247592,"uid":21305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T06:09:24.000Z","msg":"我手指公 有3份1 係月牙其他手指都好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d0ae1b43650f6d675e9223f9fc18613ee4febc4","tid":247592,"uid":8209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T06:15:55.000Z","msg":"得手指尾冇月牙 但成撚日病 體質好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01217765dde30631b07644b554fb48a40a183fc9","tid":247592,"uid":76681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T06:17:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得手指尾冇月牙 但成撚日病 體質好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n成日病不等同腎氣差，"},{"pid":"24f404c4fef1239fcd745d8108b0207e2d937ea3","tid":247592,"uid":2023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T07:02:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我手指公 有3份1 係月牙其他手指都好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無圖你話你係死神一護都得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}